title: Grateful Dead Live at Music Hall on 1971-12-02
description:
Set 1

Bertha, Playin' In The Band, Mr. Charlie, Sugaree, Beat It On Down The Line, Black Peter, Next Time You See Me, Jack Straw, Tennessee Jed, Mexicali Blues, Smokestack Lightning, Big Railroad Blues, Casey Jones, One More Saturday Night

Set 2

Sugar Magnolia, Deal, El Paso, Brokedown Palace, Uncle John's Band, Not Fade Away-> Turn On Your Love Light-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Not Fade Away, E: Johnny B. Goode

FM broadcost WBCN-Boston - Other artist(s): NRPS

reviews.review_text: Welcome back, Pig! Sounds great, total smokeshow. Smokestack Lightning is so good my head fell off. Love it.
